{{stub}}
'''Dave Rygalski''' is [[Helen Pai]]'s husband. The character of [[Dave Rygalski]] is loosely based on him. He is playing the guitar off-camera for [[Sebastian Bach]] and has a scene as an accoustic guitar player in [[6.22]].
Other than that, he is also a writer for the Jay Leno show.

